{
  "id": "635257262662b2002041fdc8",
  "title": "トイレ",
  "created": 1666340653,
  "updated": 1778492061,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "635257262662b2002041fdc8",
      "text": "トイレ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1666340653,
      "updated": 1666340653
    },
    {
      "id": "6352572c5b98c200006e0d76",
      "text": "　[トイレット]（[toilet]）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666340653,
      "updated": 1666342354
    },
    {
      "id": "635257665b98c200006e0d78",
      "text": "　[トイレ]をあらわす言葉、[隠語]は多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1666340711,
      "updated": 1778492028
    },
    {
      "id": "635257935b98c200006e0d79",
      "text": "　　[手洗い]、[便所]、[雪隠]、[お花摘み]、[厠]、[化粧室]、[はばかり]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666340756,
      "updated": 1666355338
    },
    {
      "id": "635257345b98c200006e0d77",
      "text": "　[IBM] は、[トイレの使用を予約するシステム及び方法の特許]をとった",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1666340660,
      "updated": 1666355251
    },
    {
      "id": "6365fa31b8bbfc000074a816",
      "text": "　みんなで同じところめがけて[排泄]をしようというシステムはいつからあるんだろう[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667627570,
      "updated": 1778492015
    },
    {
      "id": "6365fa63b8bbfc000074a817",
      "text": "　\t本能？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1667627620,
      "updated": 1667627629
    },
    {
      "id": "6365fa6cb8bbfc000074a818",
      "text": "　\t\t人間ではない動物もする？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1667627629,
      "updated": 1667627629
    },
    {
      "id": "636604da1280f0000034b447",
      "text": "　\t\t[タヌキ]が同じところに[うんち]する[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667630299,
      "updated": 1778492007
    },
    {
      "id": "636604e71280f0000034b449",
      "text": "　\t\t　[土手]の上でやられると、避けなければならなくて迷惑",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667630312,
      "updated": 1778492002
    },
    {
      "id": "6a01a28f0000000000597b0e",
      "text": "　\t\t[縄張り]の主張[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778492048,
      "updated": 1778492061
    },
    {
      "id": "6365fa82b8bbfc000074a81a",
      "text": "　\t家屋の発達や[下水道]の整備は関係する？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667627651,
      "updated": 1778491997
    },
    {
      "id": "636605041280f0000034b44a",
      "text": "　\t[排泄]ではないが、同じ箇所に[廃棄物]を集める点で[貝塚]が似てるかも[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667630341,
      "updated": 1778491993
    },
    {
      "id": "63661484b8bbfc00007c2257",
      "text": "　\t\t[貝塚]を連想することについて同意[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667634309,
      "updated": 1778491986
    },
    {
      "id": "636614abb8bbfc00007c2259",
      "text": "　\t\thttps://www.fcp.or.jp/mahoron/faq/faq24.htm",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1667634348,
      "updated": 1667634351
    },
    {
      "id": "63662bb0b8bbfc00002b2941",
      "text": "　\t\t[貝塚]に[うんこ]してた可能性も",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1667640241,
      "updated": 1778491984
    },
    {
      "id": "63525cf45b98c200009b6043",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1666342132,
      "updated": 1778492045
    }
  ]
}